casebody.data:
Torbett, Respondent, v. Eaton, Appellant. (Supreme Court, General Term, First Department. January 24,1890.)

Argued before Van Brunt, P. J., and Brady and Daniels, JJ.

■ Eugene H. Lewis, for appellant. W. W. Badger, for respondent.

No opinion. Motion to dismiss denied. For former report, see 1 N. Y. Supp. 614.
